statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from `abscisas` as `abs` inner join `vehiculo_transporte_material` as `vtm` on `vtm`.`id_abscisa_descargue` = `abs`.`idAbscisa` left join `vehiculo_transporte_material` as `vtmd` on `vtmd`.`id_abscisa_cargue` = `abs`.`idAbscisa` where `abs`.`idAbscisa` LIKE '%1%' and `abs`.`estadoAbscisa` = '1' group by `abs`.`idAbscisa`, `abs`.`nombre`, `abs`.`volumen_llenado_teorico`, `abs`.`volumen_excavado_teorico`, `volumen_real_llenado`, `volumen_real_excavado`

select `abs`.`idAbscisa`, `abs`.`nombre`, `abs`.`volumen_llenado_teorico`, `abs`.`volumen_excavado_teorico`, sum(vtm.cantidadMaterial) as volumenLlenado, sum(vtmd.cantidadMaterial) as volumenExcavado from `abscisas` as `abs` inner join `vehiculo_transporte_material` as `vtm` on `vtm`.`id_abscisa_descargue` = `abs`.`idAbscisa` left join `vehiculo_transporte_material` as `vtmd` on `vtmd`.`id_abscisa_cargue` = `abs`.`idAbscisa` where `abs`.`idAbscisa` LIKE '%1%' and `abs`.`estadoAbscisa` = '1' group by `abs`.`idAbscisa`, `abs`.`nombre`, `abs`.`volumen_llenado_teorico`, `abs`.`volumen_excavado_teorico`, `volumen_real_llenado`, `volumen_real_excavado` order by `abs`.`nombre` asc limit 1000 offset 0

select count(*) as aggregate from `abscisas` as `abs` inner join `vehiculo_transporte_material` as `vtm` on `vtm`.`id_abscisa_descargue` = `abs`.`idAbscisa` inner join `vehiculos_transporte` as `vht` on `vtm`.`idVehiculo` = `vht`.`idVehiculo` inner join `materiales` as `mat` on `mat`.`idMaterial` = `vtm`.`idMaterial` where `abs`.`idAbscisa` LIKE '%1%' and `abs`.`estadoAbscisa` = '1' group by `abs`.`nombre`, `vtm`.`fecha`, `vtm`.`numeroRecibo`, `vht`.`placa`, `vtm`.`cantidadMaterial`, `mat`.`nombre`

select `abs`.`nombre`, `vtm`.`fecha`, `vtm`.`numeroRecibo`, `vht`.`placa`, `vtm`.`cantidadMaterial`, `mat`.`nombre` as `matnombre` from `abscisas` as `abs` inner join `vehiculo_transporte_material` as `vtm` on `vtm`.`id_abscisa_descargue` = `abs`.`idAbscisa` inner join `vehiculos_transporte` as `vht` on `vtm`.`idVehiculo` = `vht`.`idVehiculo` inner join `materiales` as `mat` on `mat`.`idMaterial` = `vtm`.`idMaterial` where `abs`.`idAbscisa` LIKE '%1%' and `abs`.`estadoAbscisa` = '1' group by `abs`.`nombre`, `vtm`.`fecha`, `vtm`.`numeroRecibo`, `vht`.`placa`, `vtm`.`cantidadMaterial`, `mat`.`nombre` order by `abs`.`nombre` asc limit 1000 offset 0

select count(*) as aggregate from `abscisas` as `abs` inner join `vehiculo_transporte_material` as `vtm` on `vtm`.`id_abscisa_cargue` = `abs`.`idAbscisa` inner join `vehiculos_transporte` as `vht` on `vtm`.`idVehiculo` = `vht`.`idVehiculo` inner join `materiales` as `mat` on `mat`.`idMaterial` = `vtm`.`idMaterial` where `abs`.`idAbscisa` LIKE '%1%' and `abs`.`estadoAbscisa` = '1' group by `abs`.`nombre`, `vtm`.`fecha`, `vtm`.`numeroRecibo`, `vht`.`placa`, `vtm`.`cantidadMaterial`, `mat`.`nombre`
